 《石之心》在 Netflix 上播出多久？ https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-long-is-heart-of-stone-on-netflix-3481596?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-long-is-heart-of-stone- Netflix 上JJ NattrassFri, 11 Aug 2023 08:01:27 +0000 Film NewsNewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3481596 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="盖尔·加朵《石之心》" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>盖尔·加朵 (Gal Gadot) 凭借一部新的动作片成为主角</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-long-is-heart-of-stone-on-netflix-3481596">《石之心》在 Netflix 上的播出时间有多长？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="盖尔·加朵《石之心》" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Heart_Of_Stone_Gal_Gadot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>的动感十足的<em>《石之心》</em>今天（8 月 11 日星期五）登陆 Netflix - 您可以在下面找到有关其运行时间的详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/heart-of-stone-review-gal-gadot-spy-thriller-with-a-focus-on-fun-3481294">《石之心》评论：盖尔·加朵间谍惊悚片，注重乐趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>在电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/wonder-woman"><em>《神奇女侠</em></a>》中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gal-gadot">盖尔·加朵</a>再次扮演全球守护者的角色（没有超能力），扮演情报特工雷切尔·斯通。斯通的处境并不令人羡慕，她发现自己是唯一一个阻止她强大的全球维和组织失去其最有价值和最危险资产的人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/heart-of-stone-review-gal-gadot-spy-thriller-with-a-focus-on-fun-3481294"><em>NME.com</em>在评论中表示， <em>《石之心》</em></a> “比 Netflix 最近的许多内容更有趣，也更流畅”。事实上，这部三星级电影因其娱乐因素而赢得了后续拍摄的号召。</p><p>在这部快节奏的动作片中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fifty-shades-of-grey-film-gets-18-rating-for-stro-879777"><em>，《五十度灰》的</em></a>主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-dornan">杰米·多南和</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/film/crazy-rich-asians-author-kevin-kwan-has-written-a-script-for-a-movie-set-in-the-philippines-3210379"><em>《摘金奇缘》</em></a>的景露思在加朵身边演绎了颠簸、擦伤和笑点。汤姆·哈珀 (Tom Harper) 负责幕后工作，他曾执导过<em>《Aeronauts》</em>和 2016 年由莉莉·詹姆斯 (Lily James) 主演的迷你剧《<em>战争与和平》</em> 。</p><h2> <em>《石之心》</em>在 Netflix 上播出多久？ </h2><figure id="attachment_3481617" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3481617" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3481617" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Gal-Gadot-in-Heart-of-stone.jpeg" alt="《石之心》是 Netflix 的最新动作片" width="2000" height="1275" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Gal-Gadot-in-Heart-of-stone.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Gal-Gadot-in-Heart-of-stone-400x255.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Gal-Gadot-in-Heart-of-stone-800x510.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Gal-Gadot-in-Heart-of-stone-696x444.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Gal-Gadot-in-Heart-of-stone-1392x887.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Gal-Gadot-in-Heart-of-stone-1068x681.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3481617" class="wp-caption-text">盖尔·加朵在这部新动作片中饰演雷切尔·斯通。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>这部电影的官方时长为两小时零两分钟，这意味着该动作片比加朵单独饰演神奇女侠的电影更有冲击力、更快。原版 DC 电影的片长为 2 小时 21 分钟，而 2020 年的续作<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wonder-woman-1984-film-review-2839399"><em>《神奇女侠：1984》</em></a>则更长，为 2 小时 31 分钟。</p><p>在电影上映前，多南告诉<a href="https://collider.com/gal-gadot-jamie-dornan-alia-bhatt-interview-heart-of-stone/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Collider，</em></a>他对演员和工作人员在签约制作<em>《石之心》</em>时所做的事情感到特别自豪，他说：“我只是想到它的规模和雄心，希望我们能够”我们成功了。你知道，我们正在带领人们在这里进行适当的旅程，特别是，你知道，从一开始，前 15 分钟就像是，你最好做好准备。”</p><p>与此同时，加朵说：“我很高兴人们能坐在座位边上。我很高兴他们能够揭露其中的曲折。我认为这部电影中有大量的幽默、动作和戏剧，只是为了让人们享受它并与我们一起享受电影的乐趣。”</p><p>请观看下面的<em>《石之心》</em>预告片。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="石之心 |盖尔·加朵 |官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XuDwndGaCFo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-long-is-heart-of-stone-on-netflix-3481596">《石之心》在 Netflix 上的播出时间有多长？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
